The '''''Hoopster's Prank''''' was a freighter owned by [[Booster Terrik]] and used in his smuggling operations. It was often code-named '''''Sycophant Jolly'''''.

During the [[Caamas Document Crisis]] of [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] task force under the command of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Garm Bel Iblis]] used searching the ''Hoopster's Prank'' as a pretext for breaking a [[Frezh]]lix [[Blockade of Sif'kric|blockade]] of [[Sif'kric]].

